Authors@R: 
    person("Yan", "Xie", email = "xie.yanist@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements a rule-based automated method for identifying the optimal intervention impact model for interrupted time series. The approach combines the strengths of both the LTF and sequential Koyck model identification rules.
